  "EU AI Act: What Actually Applies on 2 August 2026": "EU AI Act: What Actually Applies on 2 August 2026",
  "Educational demo: HMAC-SHA256 with a shared secret, showing request-bound, expiring, verifiable license tokens. Production tokens should be signed asymmetrically, with the publisher’s public key discoverable under /.well-known/.": "Õppedemo: HMAC-SHA256 koos jagatud saladusega, mis näitab päringuga seotud, aeguvaid ja kontrollitavaid litsentsitokeneid. Tootmiskeskkonna tokenid tuleks allkirjastada asümmeetriliselt, väljaandja avaliku võtme leidmisega raja /.well-known/ alt.",
  "Eight more /topics entries, this time researched by an AI agent rather than curated by hand — same rule as before: every source fetched and confirmed live, summaries an original paraphrase, before anything gets added. 14 entries total.": "Veel kaheksa kannet jaotises /topics, seekord uuris need AI-agent, mitte käsitsi kureeritud — sama reegel nagu varem: iga allikas tuuakse ja kinnitatakse elavalt enne lisamist, kokkuvõtted on originaalne parafraas. Kokku 14 kannet.",
